  "title": "1 year Client Services Admin Support",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Provide administrative and operational support to the business development team</li><li>Maintain and update fund documents, templates, presentations, and spreadsheets</li><li>Support preparation of sales and marketing materials, including customized presentations and decks</li><li>Assist with coordination of events such as conferences, seminars, and roadshows</li><li>Maintain and organize distribution lists, client data, and internal records</li><li>Prepare basic reports, market research, competitor analysis, and support ad-hoc projects</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Bachelor’s degree in Economics, Finance, Accounting, Business, or related field</li><li>1+ years of experience in an administrative, sales support, client servicing, or team support role in the financial services industry</li><li>Strong proficiency in Microsoft Word, Excel, and PowerPoint</li><li>Detail-oriented with strong organizational and coordination skills</li><li>Self-motivated, resourceful, and able to work independently</li><li>Comfortable working with multiple stakeholders and managing changing priorities</li></ul><p>If you have what it takes, please send your resume to syafiqah@ambition.com.sg or click APPLY NOW.<br />Data provided is for recruitment purposes only. Regrettably, only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br />Business Reg No : 200611680D | Licence No : 10C5117 | EA Reg No : R2199023</p>",
